	   <tr><td colspan=2>Magi lack crowd control. It's a balance thing (per Verant). What is great, however, is to team with an Enchanter.&nbsp;&nbsp;I soloed a lot up to about 21.  At that point I found that I needed to be really careful or things got out of hand fast (no crowd control). My normal partner now is an enchanter. Having a two person group is great.  We can handle more Mobs with less downtime and he controls the crowds so extra Mobs showing up are a benefit now vs. a panic situation.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
